com.github.besherman.lifx

Interface LFXGroup

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<LFXLight>, LFXLightCollection

    public interface LFXGroup
extends LFXLightCollection
    A group of lights. This allows for multiple lights to be changed at a time. If you are changing power or color on a lot of lights at the same time the LIFX protocol only requires one message to be sent if you are using a group.
